</shortdesc><topicmeta></topicmeta></topic><topic href="02_syntax.html" data-id="t3p_nvx_dwb"><title>2 CSS语法规范</title><shortdesc><p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="shortdesc">你可以通过vscode中写几行代码来初步体验css的语法规则。</p>
</shortdesc><topicmeta></topicmeta></topic><topic href="03_selectors.html" data-id="vmt_zfx_dwb"><title>3 CSS选择器</title><shortdesc><p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="shortdesc">CSS 选择器用于“查找”（或选取）要设置样式的 HTML 元素。</p>
</shortdesc><topicmeta></topicmeta><topic href="03.1_simple_selectors.html" data-id="czh_p3x_dwb"><title>3.1 简单选择器</title><shortdesc><p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="shortdesc">下面将介绍元素选择器、id选择器、类选择器、通用选择器以及分组选择器。</p>
</shortdesc><topicmeta></topicmeta></topic><topic href="03.2_other_selectors.html" data-id="dnr_jhf_2wb"><title>3.2 CSS选择器</title><topicmeta></topicmeta></topic></topic><topic href="04_how_to.html" data-id="hb4_wv1_2wb"><title>4 如何插入CSS样式表</title><shortdesc><p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="shortdesc">当浏览器读到样式表时，将根据样式表中的信息来格式化 HTML 文档。</p>
</shortdesc><topicmeta></topicmeta><topic href="04.1_external.html" data-id="pqp_cx1_2wb"><title>4.1 外部样式表</title><shortdesc><p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="shortdesc">通过使用外部样式表，只需修改一个文件即可改变整个网站的外观。</p>
</shortdesc><topicmeta></topicmeta></topic><topic href="04.2_internal.html" data-id="yct_3cb_2wb"><title>4.2 内部样式表</title><shortdesc><p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="shortdesc">如果一张 HTML 页面拥有唯一的样式，那么可以使用内部样式表。</p>
</shortdesc><topicmeta></topicmeta></topic><topic href="04.3_inline.html" data-id="cht_j2b_2wb"><title>4.3 内联样式表</title><shortdesc><p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="shortdesc">行内样式（也称内联样式）可用于为单个元素应用唯一的样式。</p>
</shortdesc><topicmeta></topicmeta></topic><topic href="04.4_multistyle.html" data-id="r5q_xmb_2wb"><title>4.4 多个样式表</title><topicmeta></topicmeta></topic></topic><topic href="05_color.html" data-id="pwf_xfy_dwb"><title>5 CSS颜色</title><shortdesc><p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="shortdesc">CSS 支持 <strong class="ph b">140 多种颜色名称</strong>，以及十六进制值、RGB 值、RGBA 值、HSL 值、HSLA 值和不透明度。</p>
</shortdesc><topicmeta></topicmeta><topic href="05.1_color_rgb.html" data-id="hww_ljc_2wb"><title>5.1 RGB颜色</title><topicmeta></topicmeta></topic><topic href="05.2_color_hex.html" data-id="wfl_dnc_2wb"><title>5.2 HEX颜色</title><topicmeta></topicmeta></topic><topic href="05.3_color_hsl.html" data-id="sbk_knc_2wb"><title>5.3 HSL颜色</title><topicmeta></topicmeta></topic></topic><topic href="06_font.html" data-id="thf_bqb_2wb"><title>6 CSS字体</title><shortdesc><p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="shortdesc">CSS字体属性定义字体，加粗，大小，文字样式。</p>
</shortdesc><topicmeta></topicmeta><topic href="06.1_font_family.html" data-id="yyw_j5b_2wb"><title>6.1 字体系列</title><shortdesc><p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="shortdesc">在 CSS 中，我们使用 <code class="ph codeph">font-family</code> 属性规定文本的字体。</p>
</shortdesc><topicmeta></topicmeta></topic><topic href="06.2_font_size.html" data-id="ibq_rvb_2wb"><title>6.2 字体大小</title><shortdesc><p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="shortdesc"><code class="ph codeph">font-size</code> 属性设置文本的大小。</p>
</shortdesc><topicmeta></topicmeta></topic><topic href="06.3_font_weight.html" data-id="sqc_kdc_2wb"><title>6.3 字体粗细</title><topicmeta></topicmeta></topic><topic href="06.4_font_style.html" data-id="m4j_jfc_2wb"><title>6.4 字体样式</title><shortdesc><p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="shortdesc"><code class="ph codeph">font-style</code>属性指定文本的字体样式。</p>
</shortdesc><topicmeta></topicmeta></topic></topic><topic href="07_text.html" data-id="nsm_c4c_2wb"><title>7 CSS文本</title><shortdesc><p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="shortdesc">本节将介绍颜色（text color）、文本排列（text alignment）、行（line）以及字符间距（letter         spacing）等多种效果。</p>
